name: TractorER
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tractor e. r.
des:
Tractor E.R. is a trivia game about some of the tractors located at Jack's Urban Meeting Place in downtown Boise. In this game, you will be given a clue to locate one of the tractors. Once the correct tractor is located, you will be given a trivia question to answer regarding a potential issue that that particular tractor might have encountered. The game can be paused at any time, as you will be given a number when starting a game that you can use to load your game later.

While the game can be played anywhere, it is best experienced while physically located at Jack's Urban Meeting Place.
